    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Validation results demonstrate aggregate RMSE of 0.0031 g/100 L and R² of 0.97 across the five operating points, and the relative hemolysis index RH = 0.84 satisfies the RH < 1 acceptance criterion. The six non-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 3. The credibility assessment team concluded that the evidence package is sufficient to support the regulatory submission decision.",
